  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Despite being published in 2021, \"The Tacit Dimension\" has not yet garnered citations, indicating a nascent stage in its academic uptake. However, it displays strong commercial linkage through its presence on platforms like Amazon and Goodreads, suggesting potential interest among readers.</p>\n\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">\"The Tacit Dimension,\" published by Leuven University Press in 2021, has yet to receive formal citations, pointing to a developing trajectory within academic discourse. Nevertheless, this work is supported by a robust commercial presence, as evidenced by its availability on significant retail platforms such as Amazon and its listing on Goodreads. This commercial linkage reflects a foundational interest that could foster increased visibility and discussion in the future.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">As of now, there is no reported community discourse surrounding the work on platforms like Wikipedia, Reddit, or Bluesky, which suggests that the book has not yet penetrated public or social media discussions. This absence might indicate that the book is still establishing its foothold in popular or academic conversations. Hence, the potential pathways for public engagement remain to be explored.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">In terms of its relevance to broader discussions of sustainability, the work has a modest strength noted at 0.55 in policy sustainability relevance, signaling that there may be themes within the book that align with significant societal challenges, such as those outlined in the Sustainable Development Goals. However, the low engagement metrics suggest that its contributions to these discussions are not yet widely recognized.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">Ultimately, while \"The Tacit Dimension\" currently lacks citations and community engagement markers, its commercial linkage serves as a promising starting point for future discourse. The absence of empirical citations does not negate the potential for the book to become influential as it continues to attract interest among readers and scholars alike, which may foster a richer dialogue in the coming years.</p>",
